title: d'jawa
typeOfFood: Fast food, Delivery, Take-out, Indonesian, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Vegans could get the tofu satay with peanut sauce, white rice, and steamed vegetables. Many appetizers are vegan, including eggplant with tomato and chili sauce and tofu and runner-beans salad with soy sauce. The oconut milk soup with bananas and fresh fruit dessert is vegan but the chocamole dessert contains dairy milk.
